+## Findings
+
+### 1. The admissible slate is already bounded on the repository record
+
+- [VERIFIED] The exact-rewrite branch already froze a three-family shortlist:
+  `divergence / stress form`,
+  `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form`,
